Smartüs is a brand new experience by Taurus, enabled by its new line of WiFi products that brings to you the power of voice commanding through Alexa. Wondering what can you do? Here are some examples:

-Magnüs & Stardüst WiFi Fans
 "Alexa, turn on the fan"
 "Alexa, set high speed on fan"
 "Alexa, speed 1 on fan"

- Opüs smart plug
 "Alexa, turn on the smart plug"
 "Alexa, turn off the Opüs"

Or you can rename the devices to any name you want and Alexa will recognize it!

Remember to link your Alexa account from the Smartüs App, so Alexa can discover your Smartüs products.
(1) Download our “Smartüs” app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in our “Smartüs” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4) Search “Smartüs by Taurus” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5) Enable “Smartüs by Taurus” skill, and you'll be navigated to “Smartüs by Taurus” login page;
(6) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices!
